com.linecorp.armeria.client.pool

Interface KeyedChannelPool<K>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of the key, usually PoolKey
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultKeyedChannelPool

    public interface KeyedChannelPool<K>
    An asynchronous Channel pool that provides key-based acquisition and release.
